(195, NULL, '57 Billion LGSF: How Funds are Allocated to LGUs & What They Can Build', NULL, '============================================================\r\n  MBC AI Clip Generator\r\n============================================================\r\n\r\nTitle          : 57 Billion LGSF: How Funds are Allocated to LGUs & What They Can Build\r\nSource File    : Exclusive interview.mp4\r\nContent Type   : insight\r\nVirality Score : 8.8 / 100\r\nRank           : #2\r\n\r\nStart          : 03:14  (194.00s)\r\nEnd            : 04:18  (258.00s)\r\nDuration       : 01:04  (64.0s)\r\n\r\n------------------------------------------------------------\r\nHOOK\r\n------------------------------------------------------------\r\nHow will the 57 billion pesos from the LGSF be spent? Mayor Zamora breaks down the direct allocation to LGUs and the types of projects they can fund.\r\n\r\n------------------------------------------------------------\r\nWHY IT WILL GO VIRAL\r\n------------------------------------------------------------\r\nExplains the practical mechanisms of a large government fund, including specific project categories and the scale of benefits, making it highly informative for citizens.\r\n\r\n------------------------------------------------------------\r\nTAGS\r\n------------------------------------------------------------\r\n##LGSF  ##GovernmentFunds  ##LGUFunding  ##CommunityProjects  ##InfrastructurePH  ##Transparency\r\n\r\n------------------------------------------------------------\r\nTRANSCRIPT\r\n------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\nAt ayibaba, mismong sa mga local napamalan, ito download po ang that means papasukasa sa general fund ng aming mga nung sod, mga bayan at mga lalawigan. At meron ng menu na pwede ang pagmitan po niyan, ang kaitan ang gusto ng local napamalan, meron ng menu na inilalaan po ang dbm, na ito lang mga pwede namin. Pagmitan. Pagmitan ng hospital, papapin ng hospital, pagbili ng medik -elevipment, farm to barka -trades, multipurpose -building, mga debakuation center, infrastructura lang to mayor ang nakalagay sa menu. E -clippment. And also, ating supplies, meron ba? Meron din tayo ang programapul sa bigas. Oh, ang kaming pagdulong natin, sa ating mga mamanayano. So, milung milong pamilya po makikina bang sa pekat yung pondo na ibabapapo,\r\n\r\n============================================================', 1, 2, '2026-02-27 07:59:59', '2026-02-27 07:59:59', 0, 0, NULL, 1, NULL, 'uploads/thumb_ae6ccd9c89b94b25e12262e203e57fa7.jpg', NULL, 'manual', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0);

